            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><div n="1" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Deo Μηδυζει mensam <lb n="2"/><expan><abbr>C</abbr><ex>aius</ex></expan> Minutius Laetus vet<expan><ex>e</ex><abbr>ran</abbr><ex>us</ex></expan> <lb n="3"/><expan><abbr>leg</abbr><ex>ionis</ex></expan> VII <expan><abbr>C</abbr><ex>laudiae</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>iae</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>idelis</ex></expan> pro se et suis <lb n="4"/><expan><abbr>v</abbr><ex>otum</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>olvit</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>ibens</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>m</abbr><ex>erito</ex></expan> <lb n="5"/><expan><abbr>Imp</abbr><ex>eratore</ex></expan> Vespasiano VII co<expan><ex>n</ex><abbr>s</abbr><ex>ule</ex></expan> </ab></div><div n="2" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> Ἀντιοχέος τῆς πρὸς Δάφνην <lb n="2"/>τόδε δῶρον
            </ab></div></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Der Block diente wohl als Tischplatte der dedizierten mensa. (B): Dobruski, AE 1902: Z. 2: veteran(us).</p>
            </div>
